Ext.data.JsonP['Appcelerator_CLI_Release_Notes']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Appcelerator CLI Release Notes</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-43299503\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Appcelerator CLI Release Notes</h1>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-43299503_AppceleratorCLIReleaseNotes-AppceleratorCLI7.0.0.RC-17November2017\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Appcelerator CLI 7.0.0.RC - 17 November 2017</span></h2>\n    <p>Appcelerator CLI 7.0.0.RC is a major release that includes new features, improvements, and bug fixes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-43299503_AppceleratorCLIReleaseNotes-Componentversions\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Component versions</span></h3>\n    <p>The following components are shipped with CLI 7.0.0:    </p>\n    <div class=\"tablewrap\">\n        <table class=\"confluenceTable\">\n        <thead class=\" \"/><tfoot class=\" \"/><tbody class=\" \">    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Alloy    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>    <span style=\"color: #032f62;\">\n1.10.9    </span>\n    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>API Builder    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>3.0.0-19    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Cloud CLI    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>2.0.8    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    <tr>\n            <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>Titanium CLI    </p>\n            </td>\n                <td class=\"confluenceTd\" rowspan=\"1\" colspan=\"1\">\n        <p>    <span style=\"color: #032f62;\">\n5.0.14    </span>\n    </p>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n</tbody>        </table>\n            </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-43299503_AppceleratorCLIReleaseNotes-Improvements\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Improvements</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-628\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-628</a> - Improve Offline with Remote Verbiage    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Improved verbiage for offline devices    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-1130\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-1130</a> - Use node.js os.homedir to get homedir    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Improved how CLI retrieves home directory    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-1251\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-1251</a> - Remove download of hyperloop module for SDKs with pre-packaged module    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Users are no longer prompted to download the Hyperloop module as it has been integrated into the SDK core    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-1272\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-1272</a> - Alloy: remove &apos;mobileweb&apos; from config template    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p class=\"gh-header-title\">remove <tt class=\" \">mobileweb</tt> from config template    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-1275\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-1275</a> - Include appc-platform-sdk 3.*    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p class=\"gh-header-title\">Updated appc-platform-sdk to v3.0.1    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-1277\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-1277</a> - cli should replace &quot;tar.gz&quot; as it is deprecated    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p class=\"gh-header-title\">Replaced the unsupported <tt class=\" \">tar.gz</tt> format with <tt class=\" \">tar</tt>    </p>\n</li></ul></li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-1279\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-1279</a> - Include API Builder 3.*    </p>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>CLI 7.0.0 include API Builder 3.x.x    </p>\n</li></ul></li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-3 \" id=\"src-43299503_AppceleratorCLIReleaseNotes-Fixedissues\">\n        <h3 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed issues</span></h3>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-1266\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-1266</a> - async function without callback warning when downloading hyperloop    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/CLI-1280\" target=\"_blank\">CLI-1280</a> - CLI: Cannot create projects when using 7.0.0-master.11    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-43299503_AppceleratorCLIReleaseNotes-RecentReleases\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Recent Releases</span></h2>\n<ul class=\"childpages-macro \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_7.0.0.RC_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 7.0.0.RC Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.3.0.RC_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.3.0.RC Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.3.0.GA_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.3.0.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.2.4.RC_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.2.4.RC Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.2.4.GA_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.2.4.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.2.3.RC_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.2.3.RC Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.2.3.GA_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.2.3.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.2.2.GA_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.2.2.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.2.1.GA_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.2.1.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.2.0.GA_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.2.0.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.1.0_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.1.0 Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.0.0.RC_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.0.0.RC Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.0.0.GA_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.0.0.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_6.0.0.Beta_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 6.0.0.Beta Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"document-link \" href=\"#!/guide/Appcelerator_CLI_5.5.1.GA_Release_Note\">Appcelerator CLI 5.5.1.GA Release Note</a>    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=43299503\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Appcelerator CLI Release Notes"});